descriptor.name: RAISINS/KHISMISH/MANUKKA 100g
descriptor.short_desc: a raisin is a dried grape. raisins are produced in many regions of the world and may be eaten raw or used in cooking, baking, and brewing. rich in fiber, vitamins, minerals, polyphenol antioxidents. these are used in preparation of sweets, cakes, cooking and deserts.
